{"tid":1255382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（ 鼓勵文） 624經過呢個幾星期未明白的心竟踩下去，加上今日嘅失敗， 我返屋企途中已經打算去搵工重回正常生活","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T17:24:14.000Z","uid":251414,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9564f0b9cb1dfda2f5dee7ee35ed60edd28c7d90","tid":1255382,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"經過呢個幾星期之後我本來都想放棄， 尤其是經歷埋今日嘅(失敗)， 因為我係辭咗職去同中共鬥， 我好快要重回正常生活<br />\n<br />\n但直至我睇咗呢段片， 我決定 呢幾日都會繼續發夢發到7月1號， 因為喺我哋睇唔到任何希望嘅時候（ 尤其是今日624，暫時係 抗爭 運動之中最失敗嘅一次），但 外國朋友依然冇放棄唔幫我哋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2NPWoq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2NPWoq.jpg&h=5cff450f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/si-b_o_0EQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsi-b_o_0EQw&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=c0e4d943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/si-b_o_0EQw</a>"},{"pid":"f538cb9dcee73cbd1b7a610dcac984178bc2dde6","tid":1255382,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:05:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46636ce594acf3146527d69cfb9d35358a303472","tid":1255382,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0d6abfe6f8cbd23777f4db42daddbe4fb8e9a09","tid":1255382,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd1e43c70735c6145d5185420ca728f59cfdc98a","tid":1255382,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c85167f9d6d63c0752fa7309582c37ca2b70cdb","tid":1255382,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1193b485414b4c65452e484835da24a00fa7d59","tid":1255382,"uid":193415,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20